io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog.jekpro

Class JekejekePrologMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog.AbstractTerm
      • io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog.AbstractCompounds
        • io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog.jekpro.JekejekePrologMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrologElement, PrologList, PrologMap, PrologTerm, Comparable<PrologTerm>, Iterable<PrologTerm>, Map<PrologTerm,PrologTerm>

    public final class JekejekePrologMap
extends AbstractCompounds
implements PrologMap
    A PrologTerm that maps PrologTerm keys to PrologTerm values. A map cannot contain duplicate keys. Each key can map to at most one value.
    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain
